data.meta_description: Scenes include military officials saluting a formation of soldiers, bugles sounding and a band playing. Also, military officials, flag bearers and soldiers honoring the tomb of the unknown soldier. The royal family arrives in automobiles and walks to the tomb. Various scenes of Royal family and other personages honoring tomb. In addition, a shot of the dense crowd moving in the street.
